17:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"2026-yildan O'zbekistonda o'z-o'zini band qilgan shaxsning rasmiy maqomi aylanmadan 1% soliq bilan joriy etiladi — bu mamlakatdagi barcha soliqqa tortish rejimlari orasida eng past soliq stavkasi. O'z-o'zini band qilganlar yakka tartibdagi tadbirkor hisoblanmaydi: tadbirkorlarning yagona reyestrida ro'yxatdan o'tish talab qilinmaydi, hisobot minimal. Ro'yxatdan o'tish mobil ilova yoki my.soliq.uz portali orqali bir necha daqiqada amalga oshiriladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'z-o'zini band qilganlar uchun cheklovlar: yillik aylanma 1 000 000 000 so'mdan (1 mlrd, taxminan $78 000) oshmasligi kerak. 2026-yildan avvalgi 100 mln so'mlik cheklov bekor qilindi va barcha o'z-o'zini band qilganlar limit doirasida aylanmadan qat'i nazar 1% to'laydilar. Xodim yollash taqiqlangan va faoliyat turlari bo'yicha cheklovlar mavjud — aksiz tovarlarini ishlab chiqarish, ulgurji savdo va ba'zi litsenziyalanadigan faoliyat turlari bilan shug'ullanib bo'lmaydi. Maqom frilanserlar, repetitorlar, handmade ustalari, taksi haydovchilari, fotosuratchilar, uyda sartaroshlar va boshqa yakka mutaxassislar uchun ideal."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Soliq har oy keyingi oyning 15-sanasigacha my.soliq.uz yoki mobil to'lov ilovalari orqali to'lanadi. Soliq summasi bog'langan bank kartasiga tushgan mablag'lar asosida yoki daromadni ixtiyoriy deklaratsiya qilish orqali avtomatik ravishda belgilanadi. O'z-o'zini band qilganlar uchun ijtimoiy soliq (12%) va "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/ish-haqi","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"IJPH"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" to'lovi (0,1%) hisoblanmaydi, lekin bu pensiya stajining yo'qligini anglatadi — pensiya shakllantirish uchun ixtiyoriy badal to'lash tavsiya etiladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Rejimlarni solishtirish: o'z-o'zini band qilgan — aylanmadan 1% (1 mlrd/yilgacha); YaTT — aylanmadan 1% (1 mlrd gacha), aylanma cheklovisiz 4%, 10 tagacha xodim; umumiy tizimdagi MChJ — foydadan 15% + aylanma 24,72 mlrd dan ortiqda "}],["$","$La","1",{"href":"/uz/calculator/qqs","localeCookie":"$3:props:children:props:children:props:children:0:props:localeCookie","className":"text-emerald-700 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline underline-offset-2 decoration-emerald-500/40 font-medium","children":"QQS"}],["$","$1","2",{"children":" 12%. Sof marja 25% dan kam bo'lganda YaTT MChJdan foydaliroq. Yillik aylanma 1 mlrd dan kam va yollama xodimlar bo'lmaganda o'z-o'zini band qilgan — soliq yuki nuqtai nazaridan shubhasiz optimal tanlov."}]]}]]}],"$L1d"]}],"$L1e","$L1f","$L20"]}]
